    <h1>Guarantee</h1>
    <p>The service department is located at Kiev, Vadim Getman 6, Cosmopolite shopping center.</p>

    <p><span>During the lockdown in the cities that are in the red zone, the acceptance of service goods is carried out using the ""Novaya Pochta"".</span></p>
    <p><span>Service consultant working hours:</span></p>

