        <li><p>Email: service@computerShop.ua</p></li>
        <li><p>Mon-Fri: 09: 00-18: 00</p></li>
        <li><p>Sat-Sun: Day off</p></li>
    </ul>

    <p>The warranty implies free elimination of a defect that arose through the fault of the manufacturer during the warranty period, subject to the operating conditions.</p>
    <p>The confirmation of the warranty is a sales receipt or an invoice, and a warranty card indicating the order number, product name, serial number, and warranty period.</p>
    <p>The warranty period for products depends on the service policy of the manufacturer or importer.</p>
    <p>You");
