    <p>Warranty service is provided by official service centers authorized by");
            WriteLiteral(@" manufacturers.</p>
    <p>In case of finding defects in the laptop during the warranty period, you can transfer the goods for warranty repair to an authorized service center from the list of service centers.</p>
    <p>If there is no service center in your city that serves the goods, you can transfer the goods for warranty service to the TELEMART.UA store, or send us the goods through the carrier company, and TELEMART.UA will transfer it to an authorized service center.</p>
    <p>To transfer the goods to the service center, you must have a warranty card and a payment document.</p>

    <p>Below is a list of service centers from various manufacturers:</p>
    <ul>
